def load_data(path, kind='train'):
    import os
    import gzip
    import numpy as np

    """Load data from `path`"""
    labels_path = os.path.join(path,
                               '%s-labels.gz'% kind)
    images_path = os.path.join(path,
                               '%s-images.gz'% kind)

    with gzip.open(labels_path, 'rb') as lbpath:
        labels = np.frombuffer(lbpath.read(), dtype=np.uint8,
                               offset=8)

    with gzip.open(images_path, 'rb') as imgpath:
        images = np.frombuffer(imgpath.read(), dtype=np.uint8,
                               offset=16).reshape(len(labels), 784)

    return images, labels

x_train_org, y_train_org = load_data('../Project', kind='train')
x_test, y_test = load_data('../Project', kind='test')

# Model
model_mlp_linear = tf.keras.models.Sequential()
model_mlp_linear.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(512, input_shape=(784,)))
model_mlp_linear.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(256))
model_mlp_linear.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(64))
model_mlp_linear.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(10, activation='softmax'))

model_mlp_linear.compile(loss=tf.keras.losses.categorical_crossentropy,
                         optimizer=tf.keras.optimizers.Adam(),
                         metrics=['accuracy'])

classes = np.asarray(['T-shirt', 'Trouser', 'Pullover', 'Dress', 'Coat', 'Sandal', 'Shirt', 'Sneaker', 'Bag', 'Ankle Boot'])
mis_class = np.zeros(10,)
for i in range(10):
    mis_class[i] = np.sum(conf_mat_test[i, :]) - conf_mat_test[i, i]

print('---------------------')
for i in range(10):
    print('Misclassification of', classes[i], 'Class:', '\t', np.int(mis_class[i]), 'Samples')
print('---------------------')
most_miss_class_index = np.argmax(mis_class)
least_miss_class_index = np.argmin(mis_class)
print('Most Misclassification:', '\t', classes[most_miss_class_index], '(with', np.int(mis_class[most_miss_class_index]), 'Samples)')
print('Least Misclassification:', '\t', classes[least_miss_class_index], '(with', np.int(mis_class[least_miss_class_index]), 'Samples)')
print('---------------------')

                                       optimizer=tf.keras.optimizers.SGD(),

# Best Model with Normalization
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm = tf.keras.models.Sequential()
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size=(3, 3), activation='sigmoid', input_shape=(28, 28, 1)))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.2))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size=(3, 3), activation='sigmoid'))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.2))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Flatten())
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(128, activation='sigmoid'))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.2))
model_cnn_sigmoid_dropout_norm.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(10, activation='softmax'))

                                       optimizer=tf.keras.optimizers.Adam(),
                                       metrics=['accuracy'])
